{
  "stem": "1061.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, right along, I knew that my fate would be decided immediately, if I were to be left alone.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was no question in mind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Plans or no plans or experiences, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If I were to be alone, I would not survive, I knew it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and, and that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my passivity was really my complete faith in my two sisters-- their judgment, their love, and, and their protection.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and of course, we supported each other, you see.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we were, we were really, in all-- as they say, in the same boat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the support that we gave each other-- and we still had these other people around us, you see-- that sustained us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We still were running into these other people, here and there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That, that at least, that was a thread from the old life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So maybe you weren't such an absolute reject from life because there was, after all, somebody there who know you, who knew you as that other person in the other life, which was life, and this being not just torture, but some kind of inhuman, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know-- imagination couldn't paint this.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well anyhow, as I said, I was hit, and I was-- I was-- I fell right by the doorstep to the big barn.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when they came out, we found each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we walked, I don't remember how long.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was the most-- another horrendous experience, because it was so cold, and we didn't-- we couldn't relieve ourselves, and there was no food.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Finally, we, we came near a siding, railroad siding, whether it was a station or a siding or whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were cattle cars lined up on the railroad, open cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
